HEADWORD: Miscellane
<hw>Mis"cel*lane</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Miscellaneous</er>, and cf. <er>Maslin</er>.]</ety> <def>A mixture
